	map-comment "<lang:fr>Obƒçina Tolmin, Slovenija<br>Imperial College Caving Club<br>Jamarska sekcija PD Tolmin<lang:en>Tolmin, Julian Alps<br>Imperial College Caving Club<br>Jamarska sekcija PD Tolmin"
